a favorite Christmas cookie in our family. The name is Kringle The pearl sugar makes it so you need to find it. at times found at IKEA now that Maid of Scandinavia is out of business.

Rating: 4
My husband made these and, hot out of the oven- they were delicious and the kids LOVED them! He said the only thing he did differently from the recipe was he used 3 cups of King Arthur all purpose flour instead of 2 3/4 cups because the dough was too sticky.